this political moment in my lifetime.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='869102' id='t-869102'>I think many of the people
who have been working tirelessly</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='872710' id='t-872710'>to write about the causes and consequences</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='874872' id='t-874872'>of our historically 
high incarceration rates</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='877104' id='t-877104'>did not think we would see
this moment in our lifetime.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='880870' id='t-880870'>The question for us now is,
how much can we make of it?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='884653' id='t-884653'>How much can we change?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:58
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='887618' id='t-887618'>I want to end with a call to young people,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='890182' id='t-890182'>the young people attending college</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='891816' id='t-891816'>and the young people
struggling to stay out of prison</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='894926' id='t-894926'>or to make it through prison
and return home.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='898030' id='t-898030'>It may seem like these paths
to adulthood are worlds apart,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='902063' id='t-902063'>but the young people participating
