<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='906505' id='t-906505'>conveying us to adulthood,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='908430' id='t-908430'>they have one thing in common:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='910995' id='t-910995'>Both can be leaders in the work
